4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with proficiency in JavaScript and Python over 18 weeks. The program includes three classes weekly, featuring a high teacher-to-student ratio of 1:7. No prior coding skills are necessary, making it accessible to beginners. Students learn to build websites, develop algorithms, utilize APIs, and complete a personal project to showcase their skills. Classes are available in English and Spanish. Upon completion, participants receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop